a pornographyfighting christian group is 
blanketing congress with envelopes it says contain filthy 
pictures of homosexual acts from a taxpayerfunded art exhibit 
each envelope marked extremely offensive material enclosed 
holds explicit photographs and drawings from the david 
wojnarowicz tongues of flame show mounted with a 15000 federal 
grant 
