efforts in this sphere we have decided to move the hostages affair 
forward by releasing an american hostage within 48 hours on the 
basis of reciprocal move to accomplish what is required to 
accelarate the happy ending 
second we want the humanitarian move to be balanced between 
both sides this is a condition to move forward otherwise there is 
no meaning for a onesided movement we have responded to the 
behests hoping to reach a solution as proposed and on the basis of 
