the peep shows and xrated theaters of times 
square will give way to four new office towers now that the state 
has won the right to demolish 34 buildings in a longdelayed 25 
billion renewal project 
state and city officials hope that replacing the sex shops and 
other rundown buildings will revitalze the area and rout the 
