saying 
neighboring baltic states latvia and estonia themselves moving 
along a slower path toward independence wont be hurt by the 
cutoff to lithuania churilov said lithuanias supplies will now 
go to the republics of byelorussia the ukraine and russia as well 
as eastern europe he said 
