they considered environmentally responsible analysts from five 
big firms that will market the trust through their stockbrokers 
then selected the companies with the best financial records 
investors profit if the value of the stock portfolio rises 
merrill and the other brokerages make money from a 4 percent sales 
charge on investments units or shares in the trust will cost 
10 each with a minimum 100unit buy 
