during the same period a year earlier earnings for the most recent 
quarter were 140 a share before a restructuring charge stemming 
from the severance plan the company said 
digitals revenues for the period which is the companys third 
fiscal quarter totaled 326 billion up 4 percent from 313 
billion for the third quarter last year 
