quarter despite a mixed business environment 
unruh said international business was strong during the quarter 
but our us computer business which has been sluggish for the 
past two years remains weak and we are cautious about the business 
environment in general 
he said he expects benefits from last years restructuring to be 
seen in the second half of this year 
