oil futures prices rebounded strongly thursday on the new york 
mercantile exchange on news that opec had called an emergency 
meeting to discuss the recent plunge in oil prices 
on other commodity markets thursday grain and soybean futures 
rose livestock and meat were mostly higher and precious metals 
