two 
as the harbor sky turned from indigo to jetblack lifland 
declared one last recess for an hour when court reconvened he 
said he would render his opinion 
as they ran out of the courthouse for a quick dinner some 
skeptical union lawyers still werent convinced that lifland would 
opt for a trustee they were afraid that lorenzo the consummate 
